Description:
This is the famous pirate Whitebeard's fortress, but it seems the pirates decided to retreat to the sea as the navy forces got closer. 

The fortress is huge, and without a doubt, it is full of traps. But the rewards may be worth the risk. 

The navy troops will storm the fortress very soon, but you can take advantage of your superior mobility and loot it before they arrive.
DescriptionAction: Would you like to explore the fortress?
